response.overview: The Argentine, begins as Che and a band of Cuban exiles (led by Fidel Castro) reach the Cuban shore from Mexico in 1956. Within two years, they mobilized popular support and an army and toppled the U.S.-friendly regime of dictator Fulgencio Batista.
response.tagline: Everyone knows the icon. Few know the man.
response.title: Che: Part One

titles.title: 折古華拉 切28歲的革命
